type.description: The type of the custom tool call output. Always `custom_tool_call_output`.

id.description: The unique ID of the function tool call output. Populated when this item is returned via API.

call_id.description: The unique ID of the function tool call generated by the model.

oneOf.description: A JSON string of the output of the custom tool call.

items.description: A content part that makes up an input or output item.

oneOf.description: An array of output contents (images, files, text) for the custom tool call.

status.description: The status of the item. One of `in_progress`, `completed`, or `incomplete`. Populated when items are returned via API.

created_by.description: The identifier of the actor that created the item.

title: Custom tool call output
description: A custom tool call output that was returned by the tool.
